{"tid":1902416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府：公務員下週一起逐步恢復正常 各部門需自行採購口罩 上限5萬","createTime":"2020-02-28T10:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T10:47:16.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3520fb0b5f000c6f6e54fd472afcde295a9381","tid":1902416,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:16:48.000Z","msg":"政府下周起逐步恢復公共服務，內部通告列明除了醫護人員及參與前線抗疫工作之外，不會向所有公務員提供口罩，各部門可以自行採購口罩，以實報實銷原則處理，上限為五萬元。 <br />\n<br />\n其他公務員，政府指需要自行採購口罩，以實報實銷原則處理，各部門上限由五千元增至五萬元。若果部門主管對採購口罩仍有困難，可以向物流署申請額外口罩。<br />\n<br />\n公務員公會聯合會就指，目前無指引講明是否無口罩可以不上班，若有人因無口罩為由缺勤，相信會視為曠工<br />\n<br />\n非前線公務員買口罩可實報實銷　上限五萬元<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=382375&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D382375%26refer%3DShare&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJKg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=d0be38fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D382375%26refer%3DShare&h=1356128a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=382375&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"f264450c4099482c78bfff80cb4a1e120246ecc8","tid":1902416,"uid":85629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"傻嘅<br />\n病咗點返工呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊撚個咁戇鳩話冇口罩就唔返工"},{"pid":"7aa43ba29899e4c031e2f703fb00fd2c3724f11f","tid":1902416,"uid":25183,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:28:42.000Z","msg":"藥房：今次fat fat喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242918949152758000173c0eada97a76a46ceec2","tid":1902416,"uid":3161,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"一個部門五萬<br />\n分到落黎每人有幾多個<br />\n<br />\n加埋要招標 又係利益輸送"},{"pid":"80217c080fb37323b3